(firstQuint)Obtain Additional Information on Use of CorMatrix ECM (Extracellular Matrix).

 Up to 100 clinical sites will enroll subjects who have received CorMatrix ECM for pericardial reconstruction.

 The following clinical data will be collected at a single post-operative visit: - Demographic information - Pre-operative risk factors - Surgical procedure - Blood transfusion information, if applicable - Chest tube placement information - Surgical complications - Use of anticoagulation medication - Cardiac related procedures since surgical procedure - Device related adverse events.

